<br>
Dreamworld:<br>
20 mobs that give 2%/character in an hour = 40%/char or 240% AA / hour<br>
<br>
Realistic:<br>
12 mobs that give 2%/character in an hour = 24%/char or 144% AA / hour<br>
<br>
So your realistic is still 11%AA less than single boxing wizard's. And your dream numbers are just on par with the dream numbers single boxing wiz gets. So 6boxing isn't as hot as single boxing.<br>
<br>
It may work in some 6v1 pvp fights, but in 99% of EQ, it doesn't.<br>
<br>
-myz<br>
