If exp / hour is the thing... single boxing &gt; 6 boxing.<br>
<br>
Sam, you've tried hard, but it surely seems that only thing 6 boxing might be good is taking down single boxing people in PvP. Which accounts to less than 1% of EQ. <br>
<br>
